snippet.title: Nova's Adventure // SAGE 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game: https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/novas-adventure.2334/

After crashlanding on an unknown planet, Nova the Star sets out on an adventure to collect all the parts from his broken ship that was hit by an asteroid while on his way home.

Developed by Super Item Studios & The Retro Room Games
